        "created_at": "2023-05-17T13:07:24.136Z",
        "cooked": "<p>When the certificate or key is changed the operator should automatically pickup the new content the next time it tries to communicate with the FDB cluster or one of the sidecars. For the sidecars the certificate is always loaded: <a href=\"https://github.com/FoundationDB/fdb-kubernetes-operator/blob/main/internal/pod_client.go#L141-L144\" class=\"inline-onebox\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">fdb-kubernetes-operator/pod_client.go at main \u00b7 FoundationDB/fdb-kubernetes-operator \u00b7 GitHub</a> and the fdbclient should also refresh the certificate and key if it is changed.</p>",
