        "created_at": "2023-05-17T15:14:07.368Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Another question, we mount TLS cert in both operator and fdb itself.   So, it is required for operation purpose like starting and stopping the operand?  Why does it need the cert between the operator and operand as the operand only need the cert for communicate to outside.  Wouldn\u2019t it should be ok if only RBAC is there for communication and control?</p>",
